  "texts": [
    "To perform QDA, we applied the iterative coding process of Corbin and Strauss [16].",
    "Each iteration consisted of coding one document based on the three steps: open coding, axial coding, and selective coding.",
    "Open coding means annotating relevant segments of text with codes.",
    "The codes represent concepts.",
    "In the step of axial coding these concepts, called codes, have been structured in a hierarchical code system by grouping similar concepts into categories."
  ],
